Name: Wonder Bubble in the Port of Riccioli
AttributesDescription: A mysterious floating bubble where fish might be hiding. Upon purchase, a Wonder Bubble will be generated near the current dock to help Rover catch crabs and urchins.
BgDescription: Legend has it that this bubble forms from the breath of the Cetus the Tidebreaker, serving as a natural shelter for fish... until fishermen burst their bubble of sanctuary.
